  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Proflex® Mesh (partially absorbable mesh, Korea) and Marlex® Mesh (heavyweight mesh) will be
      used for inguinal hernia repair to compare the safety and efficacy (pain score, quality of
      life)of two devices at 3 months follow-up.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
